article.description: — PJ Henry had 16 points as Texas Southern defeated Grambling State 67-61 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Henry carries Texas Southern over Grambling St. 67-61
article.linkText: Henry carries Texas Southern over Grambling St. 67-61
article.story: GRAMBLING, La. -- — PJ Henry had 16 points as Texas Southern defeated Grambling State 67-61 on Wednesday night. John Walker III had 12 points and eight rebounds for Texas Southern (3-8, 1-1 Southwestern Athletic Conference). John Jones added 10 points. Amari McCray had 13 points for Grambling State (3-11, 0-1), whose losing streak reached six games. Cameron Christon added 12 points. Tra'Michael Moton had 11 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
